==English==

===Noun===
'''tafferel'''
#{{nautical}} the upper, flat part of a ship's [[stern]], so called from its carved panels.
#same meaning as [[taffrail]]

===Etymology===
From Dutch ''tafereel'', a panel, picture,  diminutive of ''tafel'', table. Dutch from the Latin ''tabula'', table.

